# Healthy Chocolate Waffles

Based on [The Ultimate Healthy Chocolate Waffles - Amy's Healthy Baking](https://amyshealthybaking.com/blog/2019/06/19/the-ultimate-healthy-chocolate-waffles) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20250918091712/https://amyshealthybaking.com/blog/2019/06/19/the-ultimate-healthy-chocolate-waffles/))

